lab.android.rwth.evgenijandkate.plugscontrolclient.model

Class PlugItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • lab.android.rwth.evgenijandkate.plugscontrolclient.model.PlugItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IListItem

    public class PlugItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements IListItem
    Created by ekaterina on 04.06.2015. An implementation of IListItem.java. The PlugItem is being used as a type of items in the plugs list adapter set for the list view, from which the user can manage the plugs. All the methods are implemented from an interface IListItem.java.
